	<p>Hmm.  I like that "solution" to the "problem" I typed in my previous post.<br />
<br />
Sorry for responding to myself, but in short:<br />
<br />
Change Leopard/Panther:<br />
1/2 current proc rate.<br />
10 max procs.<br />
No recast delay.<br />
6.0 casting time.<br />
30 minute duration.<br />
(effect: +50 melee DPS for 2 minutes for 600 mana)<br />
<br />
Change mage flame orbs:<br />
Targettable summon<br />
6.0 casting time.<br />
mana cost reduced to 600<br />
(effect: +50 spell DPS for 2 minutes for 600 mana)</p>
	
	
	
	
	
