	Joined: Dec 2001<br />
	
</span></td>
	
	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p><blockquote><span class="smallfont">Quote:</span><hr size="1" />Originally Posted by <b>Macnair</b><br /><i>You have some interesting numbers here, Yakk.  <br />
<br />
I think some of your variables provide useful side-numbers, but they don't really figure into the calculations.<br />
<br />
I think some of your numbers are roundoffs and estimates (100 dps for panthered melees instead of 92 dps; guesstimating wizard damage 'with a comfy margin'; and so on).<br />
<br />
You have not factored in efficiency:  a wizard who only has to target the mob one time and then cast the spell will be much more efficient than a shaman who has to target a melee, cast, target another melee, cast.  The shaman will lose many small fractions of time along the way.<br />
<br />
You have not factored in that the shaman's dps takes half of the fight to build to full, while the wizard's is constant across the three minutes.<br />
<br />
If we are trying to calculate the max burst damage <i>possible</i> over a 3 minute fight, then I think mana calculations are not a factor:  we will simply line up however many necros we need, to pump however much mana is lacking, to achieve this maximum.<br />
<br />
<b>What would a wizard's max burst dps be, over 3 minutes?</b><br />
<br />
I freely admit I am pretty ignorant about wizard stuff, so I went to Graffe's and read spell info and commentary from the forums there.  At a first cut (please please some of you knowledgeable people come up with better analysis):<br />
<br />
It appears that with maximum aa and focii, and the proper buffs, a wizard can chain cast the spell "Ancient: Core Fire" 23 times in 3 minutes.  Assuming that the tank can hold aggro like superglue, that the mob is fully debuffed, assuming 18 nukes land for full @ 7936, while 5 crit @ 12006 damage:  202,878 total damage = 1127 dps.  Assuming 98% efficiency (nobody is perfect):  1104 max burst dps.<br />
<br />
<b>What would a shaman's max burst dps be, over 3 minutes?</b><br />
<br />
